<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-55-1082 </DOCNO><TEXT>Automation of production processes is one of the principal directionsin improving coal preparation efficiency. The paper deals with the basictrends of automation of coal preparation plants, the tasks and functionsof automated plant control using computing devices, the experience gainedfrom the development and introduction of automation means for dense-medium,jigging, flotation, bin loading and water-slurry circuits and similarexperience with centralized plant control equipment. The main functionsand specifications of instruments used to automate coal cleaning processesare given and advantages of their utilization in preparation plants shown.</TEXT></DOC>